            <H2>Benjamin</H2><P> </P><br><P><br>Benjamin is a double orphan left with his grandmother and social workers intervened after finding the child malnourished and uncared for. He came to us allegedly two years old but physically more like a five month old.  He has been with us now several years and still has no sponsor.  He was very withdrawn when he came and has taken a long time to feel secure.  He stayed  an extra year in preschool as he needed time to master the coordination tests snd reading readiness tests. This year he started grade 2 and is mastering reading math swimming dance and is engaged in everything that is happening.  It is so good to see, He would be so grateful to have a sponsor.</P>  ">
