                    <img src="~/Content/Images/children/xl_Zechariah.jpg" style=" height:250px"
                         data-val="  <h2>Zechariah</h2>
                    <p>Birth Date: 10th August 2000</p> <p>Zechariah is half brother to Jemimah. His father died and Zechariah lived with his mother at her second husbands homestead, until she became ill and died. We did not know Zechariah as only Jemimah was sent to our Happy Overcomers Preschool. When his mother died the family wanted nothing to do with him as he had no biological connection. We visited the homestead and found the two children. He had not been able to go to school because his father’s family had no means to help his mother. He had been neglected and was a lost little boy and abused little boy.  He has had much healing to go through from neglect and abuse.  We praise God e were able to bring him through preschool and the early grades before we moved him to live near St Mary’s school where he could pursue his schooling.  We rent a one room place for him to live near the school and hope he will continue to grow and mature. He is a strong, responsible and healthy young man. He will soon complete Grade 7 and is passing well so he should move on to high school.  He is good with animal husbandry and we pray God will provide for him to continue through High School and College so that he can contribute in a leadership role for the food production in our country.</p> ">
